name: 时间Ranger
description: 时间Ranger is capable of Space-Time manipulation, allowing him to manipulate, distort or bend reality and the space-time continuum, the fabrics of reality in which all exist in. Space-time serves as the boundary of existence, separating different realities and timelines and keeping them flowing properly; distorting this boundary can cause devastating effects, causing timelines to become fluid, altering reality, even destroying all the world.
